OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774469469
OL,3,CCampaigners protest redevelopment of
OL,4,Cformer zoo site
OL,6,FA group of campaigners trying to stop
OL,7,Fthe redevelopment of the former site
OL,8,Fof Bristol Zoo Gardens in Clifton have
OL,9,Fheld a protest outside the offices of
OL,10,Fthe developer today, Wednesday, 25
OL,11,FMarch.
OL,13,F200 new homes are due to be built on
OL,14,Fthe land by independent house builder
OL,15,FAcorn Property Group.
OL,17,FThe dozens of protestors arrived at
OL,18,Fthe offices at the top of Clifton Down
OL,19,FRoad, just a short walk from the zoo
OL,20,Fsite itself this afternoon holding
OL,21,Fplaccards and chanting.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
