OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1774469469
OL,3,CCampaigners protest redevelopment of
OL,4,Cformer zoo site
OL,6,FHe added that moving the animals was
OL,7,Fthe right decision saying, "We needed
OL,8,Fto ensure that for generations to come
OL,9,Fwe could create the right spaces and
OL,10,Fright habitats for the animals."
OL,12,FHe also added that construction is
OL,13,Fexpected to start on the site in a
OL,14,Fmatter of weeks and is expected to
OL,15,Ftake about three of four years to
OL,16,Fcomplete.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
